---
const yearsExp = new Date().getFullYear() - 2012;
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="fade-in">
    <div class="section-label">
      <span class="section-label-line"></span>
      <span class="section-label-prefix">~/about</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">The person behind the code</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-content fade-in">
      <p>
        I'm a Full Stack Developer with a soft spot for the terminal, well-crafted CLIs, and the
        kind of debugging that ends in a one-line fix and a long blog post. I've worked across the
        stack for {yearsExp}+ years: <strong>TypeScript</strong> on the backend, <strong>Rust</strong>
        and <strong>Go</strong> for tooling, <strong>Python</strong> where the data lives, and
        whatever else the job needs.
      </p>
      <p>
        I write about what breaks and how I fixed it, ship small open-source developer tools, and
        maintain a personal blog that takes itself just seriously enough. I don't believe in being
        locked into one language or framework. I pick the right tool for the job and move on.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of code, I'm usually walking somewhere with a camera, looking for trees that look
        better in <strong>black and white</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="about-tags">
        <span class="about-tag">Polyglot</span>
        <span class="about-tag">CLI craftsman</span>
        <span class="about-tag">Full stack</span>
        <span class="about-tag">Open source</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-photo fade-in">
      <div class="photo-frame">
        <img src="/about-photo.jpg" alt="Walking somewhere with a camera, off keyboard" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        <div class="photo-caption">
          <span class="photo-caption-prompt">&gt;_</span>
          off keyboard, somewhere green
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.65rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .photo-frame {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px var(--color-shadow), 0 12px 32px var(--color-shadow);
  }

  .photo-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: contrast(1.04) brightness(1.02);
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .photo-frame:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .photo-caption {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark, #d4d4d8);
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85));
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .photo-caption-prompt {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 0.4rem;
  }
</style>
